r />\n<br />\nSteakland<br />\n神戶一間幾出名食牛扒，開11點就到左唔洗點排，一開門坐滿晒，師傅即場表演咁煎牛扒，有個特價午餐好抵屌，當然貴野質素會更好（利申：試左一個特價餐一個貴餐）<br />\n<br />\n元喜神拉麵（冇圖）<br />\n奈良，重點係個雞白湯，唔好叫錯，骨膠原充足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：我專食肥野，肥左唔好怪我<br />\n<br />\n來緊會再去關西，有新發現再分享<br />\n<br />\nBetween, 鍾意靚景可以花時間去白濱<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/014048_261b72ef5e34699d70fe21f6bf58e27f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F014048_261b72ef5e34699d70fe21f6bf58e27f.jpg&h=597bd241&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩， 河童拉麵d叉燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好用心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等你去完再分享"},{"pid":"26b433c40cc17a6ed66f90285fdec5538583dba4","tid":253812,"uid":41744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/011521_4fe9ca76242f5e742eb0845aaffff801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F011521_4fe9ca76242f5e742eb0845aaffff801.jpg&h=0c7bf3fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/011523_1f480c3e9fd0d26f31476a1e2e765891.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F011523_1f480c3e9fd0d26f31476a1e2e765891.jpg&h=f16b8ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/011524_f3653f662f6c9e9cf515439f370608f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F011524_f3653f662f6c9e9cf515439f370608f8.jpg&h=a1db2941&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/011526_46b465bab0a3b3381d880343f57ff660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F011526_46b465bab0a3b3381d880343f57ff660.jpg&h=fa8cc963&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/011528_24a11a79fe413bdd91f83bb869498075.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F011528_24a11a79fe413bdd91f83bb869498075.jpg&h=44ec8826&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/011546_b07b14abfcf415c2a701207cffe05235.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F011546_b07b14abfcf415c2a701207cffe05235.jpg&h=15ab312d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nPlabo<br />\n心齋橋好似有3間，食咗半熟芝士蛋糕（蘋果味同香蕉朱古力）<br />\n<br />\nHiro Kiyamachi<br />\n京都一間幾出名既燒肉，個人勁推覺得有必要試一次，不過偏貴同好多人，推佢個醃肉（唔記得咩名）<br />\n<br />\nじねん<br />\n牛油饅魚壽司，鍾意食饅魚同菠蘿油應該好岩食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基於禮貌有叫其他壽司，還好冇特別<br />\n另外，一開始去錯咗隔離一間食shabu shabu, 因為招牌好似，但意外發現臨尾個手打烏冬不得了<br />\n<br />\n河童拉麵<br />\n見到d叉燒都知咩事，肥叉燒同豚角不解釋了<br />\n<br />\nSteakland<br />\n神戶一間幾出名食牛扒，開11點就到左唔洗點排，一開門坐滿晒，師傅即場表演咁煎牛扒，有個特價午餐好抵屌，當然貴野質素會更好（利申：試左一個特價餐一個貴餐）<br />\n<br />\n元喜神拉麵（冇圖）<br />\n奈良，重點係個雞白湯，唔好叫錯，骨膠原充足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：我專食肥野，肥左唔好怪我<br />\n<br />\n來緊會再去關西，有新發現再分享<br />\n<br />\nBetween, 鍾意靚景可以花時間去白濱<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/014048_261b72ef5e34699d70fe21f6bf58e27f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F014048_261b72ef5e34699d70fe21f6bf58e27f.jpg&h=597bd241&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩， 河童拉麵d叉燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好用心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等你去完再分享</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前兩日先係神戶食完steakland<br />\ndinner食最貴個餐 <br />\n完全唔值 可以唔洗去<br />\n<br />\n首推豬一拉麵 廣川鰻魚飯<br />\n力丸燒肉（只限心齋橋店）同十二段家都唔錯"},{"pid":"7ce728fc0e1590c0dfa5429e83d200cc5553a983","tid":253812,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca2e6c16df5f125e28e8bba8c670d6b55d60863","tid":253812,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"元喜神就算啦 我覺得仲難食過一蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afc06c7702ac23f4cb7d82bcaa4e7824c56fd61","tid":253812,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:17:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>元喜神就算啦 我覺得仲難食過一蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都食左 其實係路過入去 唔算難食<br />\n應該係食唔慣"},{"pid":"9d571d1d6a0120de696c76cce6618b4116c37b71","tid":253812,"uid":113045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>元喜神就算啦 我覺得仲難食過一蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都食左 其實係路過入去 唔算難食<br />\n應該係食唔慣</blockquote><br />\n一蘭得個平字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8bbd38deae8ebb4be716adaeac82adb1c145957","tid":253812,"uid":50458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"京都JR站 上面條拉麵街<br />\n是但一間都好食"},{"pid":"621f4840066503c34611940ada3f5d9a42af45c6","tid":253812,"uid":109224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>京都JR站 上面條拉麵街<br />\n是但一間都好食</blockquote><br />\n别講笑，食過2間都係一般水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9dad47de14b4be7d18b71b4aa76a82cbbcc70af","tid":253812,"uid":113045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩， 河童拉麵d叉燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好用心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等你去完再分享</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前兩日先係神戶食完steakland<br />\ndinner食最貴個餐 <br />\n完全唔值 可以唔洗去<br />\n<br />\n首推豬一拉麵 廣川鰻魚飯<br />\n力丸燒肉（只限心齋橋店）同十二段家都唔錯</blockquote><br />\n所以steakland多數會叫人食特價<span style=\"color: red;\">午餐</span><br />\n視覺享受佔大多數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢幾間bookmarked,有機會我又試下先🙊<br />\n<br />\n最近睇到一間難波站附近燒肉店2xx任食A4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會去挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01dfe17beb566034aa871bc7914a57dc0a05c7a","tid":253812,"uid":60531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:17:33.000Z","msg":"有無壽司推介😛"},{"pid":"0d29c5accae6abe7f7a293a79a7c2fc1fe1caa33","tid":253812,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:28:59.000Z","msg":"京都車站附近行5分鐘<br />\n有間叫本家第一旭嘅拉麵<br />\n成日都要排隊，連當地人都會去排"},{"pid":"bba2815401594f95322b24c372b30ff9ec2b8077","tid":253812,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T06:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東大拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真推介但次次都冇人so我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ab0d245bf80505853409d285ff556dae561489","tid":253812,"uid":113045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東大拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真推介但次次都冇人so我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></block